long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Simply the best Influencer Engagement data extension available. Dyzio Influencer Data calculates engagement rates automatically, finds contact email address for most influencers and allows you to build a bookmark list which can be exported as a CSV. Works for both Instagram and Tiktok.
The extension is under full development and is maintained by a professional team.
